snippet.title: Kandyland | Early Development Trailer
snippet.description:
🍭WISHLIST KANDYLAND ON STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2501620/Kandyland/

Presenting Kandyland, Early in Development! We heard your feedback! 

Welcome to Kandyland, a world of sugary delights and sweet surprises where danger lurks around every corner. Can you unravel the mysteries of Kandyland and escape from the treacherous animatronics? Check out the early development trailer now to experience the wonderful world of Kandyland, where nothing could ever go wrong… 🍭
 
#KandylandSeries #SuzySnacktime #GoldenLane
